WEBVTT

00:07.640 --> 00:08.960
‎SAY NO TO PIRACY, SUPPORT ORIGINALS

01:37.040 --> 01:42.920
‎ADAPTED FROM XI XING’S NOVEL
<i>‎QUEEN CHU</i>‎ ON QIDIAN.COM

02:17.240 --> 02:20.200
<i>A group of Northern Desert killers</i>
<i>ambushed Jiu.</i>

02:20.280 --> 02:22.240
<i>They chased Jiu for dozens of li,</i>

02:22.760 --> 02:26.520
<i>until he was cornered on a cliff</i>
<i>with no way out.</i>

02:27.280 --> 02:28.800
<i>I heard he was seriously injured.</i>

02:30.360 --> 02:33.720
<i>I guess he jumped off the cliff</i>
<i>for the sake of dignity.</i>

02:53.560 --> 02:55.320
<i>I swear on General Chu's armor.</i>

02:56.880 --> 02:58.160
I will stay alive

02:59.760 --> 03:01.400
and return the armor.

03:02.480 --> 03:03.600
<i>Both.</i>

03:04.320 --> 03:05.360
<i>The armor and me.</i>

03:08.160 --> 03:09.120
<i>I give you my word.</i>

03:09.720 --> 03:10.600
CAPITAL

03:10.680 --> 03:12.440
<i>I will come back alive.</i>

03:21.360 --> 03:22.520
Jiu,

03:24.240 --> 03:25.680
you liar.

03:28.440 --> 03:30.040
Why did you break your promise?

03:50.520 --> 03:51.360
Your Highness!

03:52.000 --> 03:52.920
Your Highness!

03:53.440 --> 03:55.160
Your Highness, we received anonymous news.

03:55.240 --> 03:56.720
Those killers aren't
from the Northern Desert,

03:56.800 --> 03:58.320
but Xiaonan Prefecture.

03:58.400 --> 04:00.720
Xiao Xun declared himself king
and feared Yunzhong.

04:00.800 --> 04:02.840
So, he wanted the Northern Desert King
to be a hostage.

04:05.040 --> 04:07.040
XIAO XUN BEHIND ASSASSINATION
OF DESERT KING AND GENERAL XIE. BE ALERT!

04:12.760 --> 04:14.360
Anyone who destabilizes my state

04:17.920 --> 04:19.680
will be killed.

04:24.200 --> 04:25.200
Issue my order.

04:27.040 --> 04:29.120
All troops in Yunzhong
stand ready for war.

04:31.560 --> 04:33.120
I'll make Xiao Xun

04:35.720 --> 04:37.920
pay blood for blood.

04:43.360 --> 04:45.160
Great, no corpses were found.

04:47.480 --> 04:50.080
The Northern Desert King
died within this state.

04:51.240 --> 04:54.560
Chu Zhao lost her sharpest blade too.

04:55.520 --> 04:56.480
Tie Ying,

04:57.280 --> 04:59.920
what expression do you think she has now?

05:00.000 --> 05:01.000
Xie Yanlai is dead.

05:01.080 --> 05:02.800
The frontier troops will be demoralized.

05:03.320 --> 05:05.440
Your Majesty, a wise plan.

05:07.840 --> 05:09.000
Wise.

05:12.920 --> 05:14.800
That wasn't my plan.

05:16.320 --> 05:17.760
I have to say,

05:17.840 --> 05:20.760
Xie Yanfang's trick to find a scapegoat

05:20.840 --> 05:22.560
was really brilliant.

05:23.440 --> 05:24.480
Are you saying…?

05:24.560 --> 05:27.080
He knew Chu Zhao would go mad.

05:27.680 --> 05:31.160
He knew she would blame me for everything.

05:31.760 --> 05:37.600
However, Chu Zhao focuses
on fighting desperately against me.

05:39.360 --> 05:41.360
So, she might never realize

05:41.960 --> 05:43.280
that she's being used.

05:43.800 --> 05:45.880
Your Majesty. Your Majesty.

05:47.320 --> 05:49.280
Your Majesty, urgent report.

05:49.360 --> 05:50.560
Her Highness led frontier troops

05:50.640 --> 05:53.280
and broke through Qingyu Pass.
They're heading for Xiaonan.

05:55.640 --> 05:57.000
At last, she's coming.

05:59.560 --> 06:02.920
XIAONAN

06:11.120 --> 06:11.960
Zhao,

06:13.160 --> 06:15.040
why bother to make such a fuss?

06:16.040 --> 06:19.120
You took your elite troops
to my prefecture.

06:19.840 --> 06:21.400
Have you come to seek refuge with me?

06:22.160 --> 06:23.080
Xiao Xun,

06:23.680 --> 06:25.640
you rebelled,

06:26.400 --> 06:27.640
murdered my general,

06:27.720 --> 06:30.520
killed the enemy king,
and broke the alliance.

06:31.160 --> 06:35.200
Today, as the Grand Princess of State,
I'll punish the traitors!

06:35.840 --> 06:37.720
I have the late Emperor's edict.

06:38.800 --> 06:41.880
I'm the legitimate heir to the throne,
favored by heaven.

06:41.960 --> 06:43.960
The real traitor

06:44.040 --> 06:45.240
remains to be seen.

06:45.920 --> 06:49.120
Faking an imperial edict
is an even greater offense.

06:49.840 --> 06:51.120
Murdered your general?

06:51.920 --> 06:53.400
Killed the enemy king?

06:54.280 --> 06:57.600
You don't think
I killed Xie Yanlai, do you?

06:58.840 --> 07:01.160
You always have an excuse to condemn me.

07:01.240 --> 07:02.360
Chu Zhao,

07:03.080 --> 07:04.720
for your personal revenge,

07:05.240 --> 07:06.560
you're starting a war.

07:07.240 --> 07:10.040
You killed a general
and brought chaos on the frontier.

07:10.120 --> 07:12.360
How dare you say this is just an excuse?

07:13.480 --> 07:15.440
Soldiers, kill the traitors!

07:18.240 --> 07:19.520
-Kill!
-Kill!

07:21.440 --> 07:22.480
Kill!

07:24.840 --> 07:26.040
Charge!

07:26.120 --> 07:27.640
Charge!

08:05.600 --> 08:07.360
Xiao Xun has been captured.

08:07.440 --> 08:09.200
You should all surrender!

08:09.280 --> 08:11.880
Deng Yi, how dare you…

08:30.160 --> 08:31.520
I didn't expect that.

08:32.120 --> 08:33.280
Deng Yi helped me win.

08:34.520 --> 08:35.640
He also made me lose.

08:36.559 --> 08:38.520
I'm the one who defeated you.

08:45.800 --> 08:46.640
<i>From now on,</i>

08:47.320 --> 08:49.240
<i>you'll be the dowager.</i>

08:49.320 --> 08:51.000
<i>Just enjoy a great life.</i>

08:51.080 --> 08:53.120
<i>Oh, my silly son.</i>

08:53.200 --> 08:56.200
A mother cares nothing for a great life.

08:56.280 --> 08:59.640
All I want is that you can stay safe.

09:00.240 --> 09:01.920
This is the talisman I got for you.

09:02.560 --> 09:04.080
You will stay healthy

09:04.160 --> 09:07.120
and watch me rise to a position

09:07.200 --> 09:08.840
second only to the Emperor.

09:08.920 --> 09:11.480
Chu Zhao had the talisman sent to me.

09:12.160 --> 09:13.320
She's threatening me.

09:14.240 --> 09:16.880
Then what will you do, My Lord?

09:18.440 --> 09:19.640
What can I do?

09:20.320 --> 09:22.960
With this talisman, she's warning me

09:23.760 --> 09:25.360
that my mother is alive

09:26.480 --> 09:28.000
and she has her.

09:38.160 --> 09:39.320
Zhao,

09:41.160 --> 09:43.080
I have true feelings for you.

09:44.200 --> 09:46.000
I never meant to hurt you.

09:46.080 --> 09:47.160
Is that so?

09:49.080 --> 09:50.600
Then in my past life,

09:51.760 --> 09:53.560
who strangled me

09:55.160 --> 09:57.360
with white silk?

10:01.040 --> 10:02.640
Your… Your past life?

10:09.520 --> 10:10.600
Yes.

10:12.440 --> 10:13.800
I lived once before.

10:15.920 --> 10:17.960
I died too.

10:20.560 --> 10:22.680
You killed me.

10:24.280 --> 10:25.560
Why?

10:25.640 --> 10:28.200
Why did you do this to my clan?

10:28.280 --> 10:30.840
Why did you do this to me? Why?

10:40.880 --> 10:42.520
Are you scared?

10:45.480 --> 10:46.680
In my past life,

10:47.400 --> 10:49.000
when you massacred my clan

10:49.840 --> 10:52.160
and cut off my father's head,

10:52.240 --> 10:54.280
you weren't this cowardly.

10:55.360 --> 10:57.760
What past life? This is ridiculous.

10:58.600 --> 11:00.960
How could anyone be reborn?

11:01.040 --> 11:03.880
Zhao, that must be a dream.

11:04.600 --> 11:07.160
You can't hate me for an illusory dream.

11:07.240 --> 11:08.800
-Zhao.
-It wasn't a dream.

11:10.040 --> 11:12.560
It was a purgatory I truly experienced.

11:14.120 --> 11:15.920
Illusory?

11:18.800 --> 11:20.360
My pain was real.

11:21.440 --> 11:23.440
My father's blood was real.

11:24.720 --> 11:25.720
Zhao.

11:25.800 --> 11:29.280
It was true that all my clansmen suffered!

11:31.440 --> 11:32.280
Zhao.

11:45.120 --> 11:47.200
You never meant to hurt me?

11:51.840 --> 11:53.520
You hated me badly

11:54.720 --> 11:56.600
<i>-and wanted my father dead.</i>
-No.

11:56.680 --> 11:58.160
<i>You wanted my clan dead.</i>

12:11.160 --> 12:14.080
You only love the throne, power,

12:15.120 --> 12:16.400
and yourself.

12:17.520 --> 12:19.160
Go to the underground

12:20.160 --> 12:21.400
with your hypocrisy.

12:36.720 --> 12:37.800
Xiao Xun,

12:38.600 --> 12:39.880
for all the civilians

12:40.520 --> 12:42.160
who suffered because of you…

12:47.440 --> 12:48.640
For my father.

12:50.160 --> 12:51.360
For Jiu.

12:53.680 --> 12:54.880
And for me.

12:56.040 --> 12:56.960
Xiao Xun,

12:58.720 --> 13:00.800
you must die.

13:07.640 --> 13:09.720
Xie Yanlai

13:11.000 --> 13:11.960
wasn't killed…

13:14.200 --> 13:15.800
In the third year of Xingping,

13:16.320 --> 13:17.800
Xiao Xun, the Prince of Xiaonan,

13:18.720 --> 13:21.160
got General Xie Yanlai killed.

13:21.240 --> 13:24.880
He colluded with enemies,
trying to ruin the State of Chu!

13:25.480 --> 13:27.600
As the Grand Princess,

13:29.000 --> 13:31.560
I'm executing him to serve justice!

14:43.520 --> 14:44.600
You picked the wrong side.

14:45.400 --> 14:48.520
A loser like me won't argue.

14:48.600 --> 14:50.120
You may die with ease.

14:51.280 --> 14:52.560
Your mother is innocent.

14:53.240 --> 14:54.160
I'll take care of her.

14:58.280 --> 14:59.760
Your Highness, I beg you

15:01.080 --> 15:03.240
not to tell her what becomes of me.

15:11.920 --> 15:12.880
All right.

15:26.160 --> 15:27.760
Your Highness,

15:28.800 --> 15:31.600
thank you!

15:35.000 --> 15:38.200
XIAONAN

15:38.280 --> 15:41.160
The Xiao Clan will be reduced to commoners

15:41.680 --> 15:42.880
and exiled to the frontier.

15:54.400 --> 15:56.920
XIAONAN

15:59.560 --> 16:04.200
XIAONAN

16:24.160 --> 16:28.160
Xie Yanlai wasn't killed…

16:31.640 --> 16:32.560
Your Highness.

16:35.280 --> 16:37.600
Your Highness, what's wrong?

16:38.280 --> 16:39.800
Before Xiao Xun died,

16:42.200 --> 16:43.800
he said he didn't kill Jiu.

16:44.880 --> 16:45.720
Le,

16:46.800 --> 16:48.120
is it possible that…?

16:48.200 --> 16:50.080
That traitor was still deceitful
even before dying.

16:50.160 --> 16:51.800
How could you believe him?

16:57.040 --> 16:58.760
But I feel something is not right.

16:59.560 --> 17:01.880
Your Highness, you're overthinking.

17:01.960 --> 17:04.760
Shall we rest early tonight?
Let me help you.

17:09.000 --> 17:11.760
Your Highness, Mr. Zhu is out there
with a report to make.

17:12.520 --> 17:13.560
Show him in.

17:20.839 --> 17:21.720
Greetings.

17:23.200 --> 17:25.800
You asked me to investigate
the Wangcheng case.

17:25.880 --> 17:29.400
We found a suspicious merchant
named Yu Shang.

17:30.000 --> 17:31.120
Go on.

17:31.200 --> 17:34.320
He runs a small business
with little contact with big merchants.

17:34.400 --> 17:36.040
But he's very friendly.

17:36.560 --> 17:38.600
Many people in town remember him.

17:42.880 --> 17:44.120
When Yu Shang left the Capital,

17:44.200 --> 17:48.040
he was holding a bottle of wine,
known as "Immortal Wine".

17:48.720 --> 17:51.800
During those days, we searched
all the taverns and teahouses.

17:51.880 --> 17:54.200
We even checked the banquets of big clans.

17:54.880 --> 17:56.240
It seemed an impossible job.

17:56.760 --> 17:57.920
But we succeeded.

17:58.520 --> 18:00.720
Those days, Yu Shang went to some taverns.

18:00.800 --> 18:03.680
In one of the taverns,
Liang Qiang was there.

18:03.760 --> 18:06.600
More importantly, a waiter witnessed

18:06.680 --> 18:09.320
Yu Shang meeting Xie Yanfang
in a private room

18:09.400 --> 18:10.960
on the second floor of Lianchi House.

18:13.840 --> 18:14.720
Xie Yanfang?

18:15.600 --> 18:17.360
Maybe that was a coincidence.

18:17.440 --> 18:20.640
We're also carefully investigating
other guests who were there.

18:20.720 --> 18:22.480
But too much time has passed.

18:23.120 --> 18:24.000
We can't recover all details.

18:28.480 --> 18:29.440
Not a coincidence.

18:30.200 --> 18:34.120
He was involved with two key figures,
Yu Shang and Liang Qiang.

18:35.280 --> 18:36.960
It couldn't be a coincidence.

18:38.080 --> 18:39.560
I'm afraid everything was…

18:46.880 --> 18:49.160
That was a really marvelous plan.

18:49.240 --> 18:50.720
Xiao Xun and Deng Yi are dead.

18:50.800 --> 18:52.360
So is Xie Yanlai.

18:52.880 --> 18:55.760
Now, the Grand Princess
stands alone. No threat.

18:56.360 --> 18:59.000
You only need to seize her command
of the frontier troops.

18:59.080 --> 19:00.880
And His Majesty trusts you.

19:01.480 --> 19:05.360
Your position is secure,
as the ruler of the world.

19:05.880 --> 19:09.600
For me, controlling the game
is what matters

19:10.600 --> 19:12.880
more than being the ruler of the world.

19:13.720 --> 19:16.000
Only those blinded by hatred

19:17.600 --> 19:21.360
would fail to see such an obvious flaw.

19:22.320 --> 19:25.440
I wonder when the Grand Princess
will find out

19:25.520 --> 19:28.080
that I am behind

19:29.400 --> 19:30.560
all of this.

19:31.680 --> 19:33.680
But by then,

19:35.000 --> 19:36.840
she will have no choice

19:38.720 --> 19:41.320
but to return to me.

19:46.600 --> 19:47.640
General Liang,

19:48.360 --> 19:51.240
how does it feel to be a prisoner again?

19:54.640 --> 19:56.040
What are you trying to say?

19:57.760 --> 19:58.600
Just say it.

19:59.240 --> 20:02.240
The day you got your title,
did you see Xie Yanfang?

20:08.120 --> 20:09.280
I knew it.

20:09.800 --> 20:13.320
At that banquet, he toasted me from afar.

20:14.080 --> 20:15.200
Only then did I know

20:17.200 --> 20:19.480
he was the one who had been helping me

20:20.720 --> 20:22.040
in the past few years.

20:22.800 --> 20:24.520
I didn't know that before.

20:24.600 --> 20:25.720
-Didn't?
-I…

20:25.800 --> 20:28.960
At Xinggu Pass,
you let the enemy troops in

20:29.040 --> 20:31.760
so that Wangcheng was lost
and your comrades died.

20:31.840 --> 20:33.160
You didn't know?

20:34.240 --> 20:35.680
You could have rejected the toast,

20:36.320 --> 20:37.360
exposed his scheme,

20:37.440 --> 20:40.400
or even have died in the battle
to prove loyalty.

20:41.600 --> 20:43.640
But you chose the dirtiest way.

20:43.720 --> 20:46.320
I just wanted to make a name for myself.

20:46.400 --> 20:48.240
The Xie Clan held great power.

20:49.480 --> 20:50.320
If I rejected him…

20:50.400 --> 20:53.160
You had countless chances to turn back.

20:55.240 --> 20:56.400
But after all,

20:57.720 --> 20:59.800
you betrayed those who trusted you.

21:07.600 --> 21:08.560
Today,

21:10.200 --> 21:12.960
I'll question you for the soldiers
who died unjustly.

21:14.440 --> 21:16.040
How does it feel

21:17.120 --> 21:17.960
to be promoted?

21:31.920 --> 21:33.240
Soldiers in Wangcheng

21:34.280 --> 21:35.640
never knew

21:38.520 --> 21:40.800
their comrade had betrayed them
even before death.

22:08.200 --> 22:09.240
I…

22:12.960 --> 22:15.560
I've learned my lesson.

22:26.840 --> 22:28.720
Liang Qiang killed himself last night.

22:29.640 --> 22:30.840
He got what he deserved.

22:36.320 --> 22:37.240
Jiu,

22:39.160 --> 22:41.400
wait and see. I will make him

22:43.200 --> 22:45.640
pay for everything he has done.

22:50.400 --> 22:53.320
Xie Yanfang always has a backup plan.

22:54.360 --> 22:55.560
The autumn hunt is coming.

22:56.240 --> 22:58.960
He will bring this up in the court.

22:59.720 --> 23:00.840
On the day of the hunt,

23:01.640 --> 23:03.160
he will make his move.

23:03.240 --> 23:05.320
Then we should make early preparations.

23:06.000 --> 23:07.080
Your Highness…

23:07.800 --> 23:10.200
Have the Longwei Army
ambush in the hunting ground.

23:12.080 --> 23:13.080
This time,

23:14.720 --> 23:17.800
I'll show him how his trap

23:19.600 --> 23:21.000
will be crushed.

23:26.680 --> 23:29.080
Mr. Deng has just died.
His Majesty is young.

23:29.160 --> 23:32.000
We need to make up
for the Regent's absence.

23:32.080 --> 23:33.440
I believe

23:33.960 --> 23:36.200
Mr. Xie is the best choice.

23:37.360 --> 23:40.280
-I second that.
-I second that.

23:40.360 --> 23:41.840
-I second that.
-I second that.

23:46.440 --> 23:47.840
Mr. Xie is virtuous and talented.

23:48.520 --> 23:49.640
He's worthy of this.

23:53.960 --> 23:56.400
Your Highness works hard to command
the frontier troops.

23:57.000 --> 24:00.360
I'll work together with you
to assist His Majesty.

24:01.840 --> 24:03.400
The autumn hunt is coming.

24:03.920 --> 24:07.040
Why don't we pray
for His Majesty during the hunt?

24:08.040 --> 24:09.400
To hunt in this season,

24:09.480 --> 24:11.600
-I'm afraid…
-When the late Emperor lived,

24:11.680 --> 24:13.360
he loved the autumn hunt

24:13.880 --> 24:15.800
to demonstrate our military might.

24:18.240 --> 24:19.320
What do you think, Your Highness?

24:20.360 --> 24:21.560
Mr. Xie,

24:23.160 --> 24:24.080
it's a good idea.

24:33.280 --> 24:35.160
CHU

24:37.160 --> 24:38.600
Yu, don't be scared.

24:39.200 --> 24:42.040
When you're around, I won't be scared.

24:42.120 --> 24:43.360
Even if I'm away

24:43.440 --> 24:45.960
and you're all alone, don't be scared.

24:46.720 --> 24:48.320
Because you've grown up.

24:48.400 --> 24:49.440
You can protect yourself,

24:49.520 --> 24:52.160
and you're the Emperor
who protects his people.

24:53.040 --> 24:56.080
Come on, Yu.
Show me how well you can hunt.

25:17.600 --> 25:19.440
Yu rides very well.

25:21.480 --> 25:22.960
But he isn't good at archery.

25:23.040 --> 25:25.240
An emperor doesn't need all skills.

25:25.320 --> 25:26.520
He just needs to keep fit.

25:27.720 --> 25:29.960
It's said you excel in riding and archery.

25:30.040 --> 25:31.360
Why don't you be his model?

25:31.440 --> 25:34.240
Since Yu was little, he has admired you.

25:34.320 --> 25:36.040
All I seek in my life

25:36.760 --> 25:39.160
is to help him become
an unparalleled emperor.

25:40.680 --> 25:41.720
Whether I can be his model,

25:43.360 --> 25:45.920
and whether my clan can remain unmatched…

25:46.880 --> 25:47.880
Neither of those matters.

25:49.760 --> 25:54.320
I know you care for Yu
as well as our state.

25:54.400 --> 25:57.840
For the court's long-term interests,
I want to issue a ban.

25:57.920 --> 25:59.440
Ban imperial in-laws from official posts.

26:00.160 --> 26:02.560
Mr. Xie, what do you think?

26:03.080 --> 26:04.080
Very good.

26:05.080 --> 26:06.280
Don't you think this is hegemony?

26:06.960 --> 26:11.800
In my heart, you will help Yu
dominate the entire world.

26:11.880 --> 26:14.200
But I don't think this is hegemony.

26:14.720 --> 26:17.360
It's what you should do
and what you have to do.

26:18.000 --> 26:19.840
I pledge my life

26:20.480 --> 26:22.120
to help you achieve this goal.

26:22.960 --> 26:24.160
It has never changed.

26:26.600 --> 26:29.320
In that case, why did you kill my ally?

26:38.760 --> 26:44.120
Who do you refer to?
Deng Yi or Zhong Changrong?

26:45.080 --> 26:46.480
Or my brother Yanlai?

26:49.680 --> 26:51.160
Deng Yi and I fell out

26:51.920 --> 26:53.680
because of the loss of Wangcheng.

26:54.440 --> 26:55.800
Or even earlier.

26:56.320 --> 26:58.840
Because Deng Yi
insisted on appointing Liang Qiang.

27:00.040 --> 27:01.240
But now it seems

27:01.760 --> 27:03.000
that Liang Qiang was your mole.

27:03.800 --> 27:06.480
So, Deng Yi was within your plan.

27:06.560 --> 27:07.400
That's right.

27:08.320 --> 27:10.440
Liang Qiang has always served me.

27:11.520 --> 27:13.960
At Xinggu Pass,
if he had killed Zhong Changrong

27:14.640 --> 27:15.680
and replaced him,

27:16.200 --> 27:18.320
it would have saved me a lot of trouble.

27:18.400 --> 27:20.800
Sadly, Yanlai interfered.

27:21.560 --> 27:23.320
My foolproof plan

27:24.240 --> 27:25.640
ended in ruin.

27:27.200 --> 27:28.240
So,

27:30.080 --> 27:31.120
he had to die.

27:33.080 --> 27:36.040
Then you sent your men
to kill him and the enemy king?

27:38.280 --> 27:40.880
Xiao Xun was a perfect scapegoat.

27:40.960 --> 27:42.320
Why wouldn't I?

27:43.160 --> 27:45.880
Xiao Xun killed the enemy king
and my brother Yanlai.

27:45.960 --> 27:47.520
There was solid evidence.

27:48.480 --> 27:51.360
That you massacred Xiaonan
to avenge Yanlai

27:51.440 --> 27:53.000
is also known to all.

27:53.600 --> 27:56.080
Now, even if you expose the truth,

27:57.400 --> 27:59.000
who would believe you?

28:01.200 --> 28:02.640
I know.

28:03.760 --> 28:06.560
Your Highness and Deng Yi
only differed in politics,

28:06.640 --> 28:08.520
but you had to kill him yourself.

28:09.400 --> 28:12.360
Deep in your heart,
you felt a little bit sad.

28:13.200 --> 28:16.640
But the two of you
couldn't coexist in the court.

28:17.240 --> 28:18.880
So for your own good,

28:19.960 --> 28:21.720
Deng Yi had to die.

28:22.480 --> 28:24.040
Even so,

28:25.480 --> 28:27.480
you shouldn't have interfered.

28:31.360 --> 28:32.600
I was helping you.

28:34.200 --> 28:35.080
No need!

28:35.600 --> 28:38.000
Xie Yanfang, I'm not your plaything.

28:38.920 --> 28:40.760
I'm different from those you have tamed.

28:40.840 --> 28:43.840
I won't become a puppet
under your control.

28:45.280 --> 28:46.840
Don't think you've won.

28:47.840 --> 28:51.600
Because this game isn't over yet.

28:53.160 --> 28:54.400
Unless I'm dead,

28:55.040 --> 28:57.640
you can never command the frontier troops.

29:01.440 --> 29:03.880
You've already lost, Your Highness.

29:04.680 --> 29:06.880
A ruler must not have weak spots.

29:07.640 --> 29:10.320
You show mercy
to so many trivial people and things.

29:11.280 --> 29:12.800
You're bound to lose.

29:21.880 --> 29:25.400
Xie Yanfang, what exactly do you want
from this trap of yours?

29:26.960 --> 29:29.200
-The frontier troops.
-No way.

29:47.960 --> 29:49.280
I'm not in a hurry.

29:50.400 --> 29:52.240
Take your time to think it over.

29:53.160 --> 29:55.080
But if you insist on refusing,

29:55.160 --> 29:57.520
tomorrow, the whole world will know,

29:58.040 --> 29:59.400
"The Grand Princess was assassinated
during the hunt,

30:00.800 --> 30:01.880
and before death,

30:02.480 --> 30:04.800
Her Highness entrusted the Xie Clan
with the military power."

30:05.520 --> 30:06.760
Xie Yanfang,

30:09.000 --> 30:10.120
you'll regret this.

30:11.440 --> 30:12.560
Regret?

30:16.440 --> 30:17.920
I won't regret anything.

30:19.080 --> 30:20.560
Nor will you.

30:22.080 --> 30:23.520
-Du Qi.
-Here.

30:24.120 --> 30:26.600
Send Her Highness back to her tent.

30:27.280 --> 30:28.800
She must be tired.

30:48.440 --> 30:52.600
Yu, this is venison from today's hunt.
Eat while it's hot.

30:53.600 --> 30:55.120
Are you going to kill Zhao?

31:01.880 --> 31:03.360
What makes you say that?

31:03.440 --> 31:06.880
I'm young, but I'm not stupid.

31:07.720 --> 31:09.000
Zhao is confined.

31:09.520 --> 31:11.080
There are unusual troop moves.

31:11.640 --> 31:12.960
Do you really think

31:13.640 --> 31:15.080
I know nothing?

31:17.840 --> 31:19.000
Your Majesty,

31:21.480 --> 31:23.200
I just want to show Her Highness

31:23.800 --> 31:26.520
that some methods just won't work.

31:27.480 --> 31:30.240
If you can persuade Her Highness
to give me the Token,

31:31.280 --> 31:32.360
I promise you

31:32.880 --> 31:34.840
she will be safe.

31:36.200 --> 31:37.520
She's my sister!

31:38.040 --> 31:39.560
The Grand Princess of State!

31:39.640 --> 31:41.400
You… You…

31:42.080 --> 31:43.760
Are you forcing me to make my choice?

31:44.960 --> 31:46.160
You're wrong.

31:48.880 --> 31:51.280
It's Her Highness who will make
her own choice.

31:51.880 --> 31:53.440
To keep the military power

31:55.240 --> 31:56.920
or to keep alive.

32:06.600 --> 32:08.880
I await your decision, Your Majesty.

32:34.760 --> 32:36.920
Zhao, I brought you some pastries.

32:37.440 --> 32:38.360
Yu?

32:38.880 --> 32:40.120
Why are you here?

32:40.200 --> 32:42.440
It's cold at night.
You should have worn more.

32:43.040 --> 32:44.760
Zhao, are you hurt?

32:45.920 --> 32:47.720
I'm fine. Don't worry.

32:49.280 --> 32:50.920
I don't want you to be confined.

32:51.680 --> 32:54.360
Let's give the Token to Uncle Yanfang.

32:57.960 --> 33:01.920
Yu, do you know the meaning
of the Frontier Troops Token?

33:02.440 --> 33:05.320
Xie Yanfang represents the Xie Family.

33:06.640 --> 33:09.720
If he seizes the military power
and allows his clan to dominate,

33:10.240 --> 33:11.480
it will be a total disaster.

33:12.120 --> 33:13.600
I just want you to live.

33:14.120 --> 33:15.240
He promised me.

33:16.040 --> 33:17.440
As long as you meet his conditions…

33:18.240 --> 33:19.080
Don't worry.

33:20.280 --> 33:21.640
We'll both be all right.

33:22.400 --> 33:23.400
Someone will come to save us.

33:24.480 --> 33:26.800
Who are you waiting for, Your Highness?

34:03.840 --> 34:05.400
You guessed right.

34:07.040 --> 34:09.600
The Longwei Army is invincible.

34:10.440 --> 34:12.600
They live incognito
and kill without a trace.

34:13.199 --> 34:16.400
Sadly, since you became the Grand Princess

34:16.480 --> 34:18.480
and the Longwei Army turned up,

34:19.199 --> 34:21.000
I have been investigating them.

34:22.719 --> 34:24.960
It took me a lot of time.

34:26.320 --> 34:27.679
But now,

34:30.960 --> 34:33.360
I know who they are.

34:35.000 --> 34:38.120
So, I cut off their heads
one after another

34:38.719 --> 34:42.480
and took off the yellow ribbons
as proof of their identities.

34:49.840 --> 34:51.639
You recognize this, don't you?

35:02.280 --> 35:03.360
You monster!

35:06.120 --> 35:07.000
-Zhao!
-You…

35:07.080 --> 35:08.920
You will pay for this!

35:09.440 --> 35:10.400
Me?

35:11.400 --> 35:13.320
They all died because of you.

35:14.640 --> 35:15.600
Not just them.

35:16.440 --> 35:18.280
If you really disobey,

35:19.160 --> 35:21.080
I'll also massacre Cangmu Stronghold

35:21.720 --> 35:24.760
and bring you the heads
of Xiaoman and her men.

35:25.560 --> 35:27.040
What do you say?

35:29.920 --> 35:32.760
Your Highness, surrender.

35:32.840 --> 35:34.840
Why don't you just kill me?

35:35.680 --> 35:36.840
Then you will have

35:37.360 --> 35:40.160
the court and the frontier troops!

35:56.000 --> 35:57.280
If you die,

35:59.480 --> 36:01.280
Yu will be very sad.

36:15.000 --> 36:16.120
Anyway,

36:17.560 --> 36:20.240
I'm waiting for you

36:20.760 --> 36:22.360
to surrender of your own will.

36:59.480 --> 37:01.120
IMPERIAL ORDER

37:05.480 --> 37:07.280
The frontier troops and Mr. Zhong

37:09.800 --> 37:11.080
only obey this token.

37:26.840 --> 37:29.640
‎FRONTIER TROOPS TOKEN

37:58.040 --> 37:59.920
This dagger is coated
with Golden Finch Venom.

38:00.000 --> 38:02.160
Xie Yanfang, you'll die!

38:10.880 --> 38:13.080
Well, you've grown.

38:14.280 --> 38:15.720
You've even learned to use poison.

38:16.680 --> 38:18.800
There's no antidote for this poison.

38:19.320 --> 38:21.760
Xie Yanfang, you're going to die!

38:22.800 --> 38:25.640
You would sacrifice your own life
just to kill me?

38:25.720 --> 38:26.640
Yes!

38:27.440 --> 38:29.280
I want you dead!

38:37.800 --> 38:39.320
Zhao, run!

38:40.160 --> 38:42.560
-Your Majesty.
-I order you to drop your weapons!

38:57.920 --> 39:00.400
This breaks my heart.

39:05.080 --> 39:06.320
Seize her.

39:08.160 --> 39:09.880
Dead or alive.

39:09.960 --> 39:11.360
-Yes!
-Yes!

39:12.400 --> 39:13.240
Your Majesty.

39:53.240 --> 39:55.080
-Stop!
-Don't run!

39:56.320 --> 39:57.920
-Stop!
-Stop right there!

39:58.000 --> 39:58.960
Stop!

39:59.760 --> 40:00.600
Hurry!

40:00.680 --> 40:03.640
-Stop running!
-Stop!
